 {"question": "Is Lusha GDPR compliant?", "answer": "Lusha is GDPR compliant and ISO 27701 certified. They maintain opt-out lists and process data deletion requests. Their community-sourced model does raise occasional privacy questions, but the company has invested heavily in compliance infrastructure since 2021."},
