 {"title": "Unlimited contacts on higher-tier plans", "detail": "Pro and Enterprise plans offer unlimited contact searches, which removes the per-credit math that makes tools like Lusha and RocketReach expensive at scale. SDR teams doing 100+ lookups per day get predictable costs regardless of volume."},
 {"title": "Built-in AI writing assistant", "detail": "smooth.AI includes an AI-powered writing tool that generates personalized email copy based on prospect data. It's not a replacement for a dedicated copywriting tool, but it saves reps 5-10 minutes per prospect on initial outreach drafts. The writing quality is adequate for first-touch cold emails."},
