 {"title": "Aggressive sales tactics and difficult cancellation", "detail": "smooth.AI's own sales process is a frequent complaint. Extended demo calls, high-pressure closing, and contracts with auto-renewal clauses that are hard to cancel. Multiple review sites flag this as a consistent issue. Read the contract terms carefully before signing."},
