 {"title": "Search results can be slow and inconsistent", "detail": "Because smooth.AI searches in real time rather than querying a pre-built database, some searches take 10-30 seconds to return results. Batch searches can take minutes. Results for the same query can differ between searches as the system hits different data sources."},
