 {"question": "How much does smooth.AI cost?", "answer": "The free plan includes 50 credits. Basic starts at $147/month with 250 credits. Pro and Enterprise plans are custom-priced and include unlimited searches. Annual contracts are standard for Pro and above. Expect to pay $2,000-$5,000/year for individual use and $10,000-$30,000/year for teams, depending on features and seats."},
 {"question": "Is smooth.AI better than Apollo?", "answer": "For most teams, no. Apollo provides a larger verified database, built-in sequencing, a dialer, and LinkedIn integration starting at $49/month. smooth.AI's real-time search model can surface fresher data in specific scenarios, but the inconsistent accuracy and higher price point make Apollo the better all-around choice. smooth.AI's unlimited plan may make sense for teams doing 100+ lookups per rep daily."},
